Class AbstractDriveCommand<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • drive.AbstractDriveCommand<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type execute() will return.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandBatch, GiveViewAccess, ReadFileList, ReadUserList, ShareFiles, UpdateDownloadAccess

    public abstract class AbstractDriveCommand<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The AbstractDriveCommand class serves as the base for custom commands meant to interact with the Google Drive or any files contained therein.
